name: VNVideoProcessingOption
desc: Options to pass to the video processor when adding requests.

items.name: static let frameCadence: VNVideoProcessingOption
items.desc: A value that indicates the video frame cadence at which to perform the video processing.

items.name: static let timeInterval: VNVideoProcessingOption
items.desc: A value that indicates that the video processor should perform a request every n-seconds.

items.name: init(rawValue: String)
items.desc: Creates an option with a string value.
